<title type="html"><![CDATA[Perfect Your Worship of Allaah Wherever You Are]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=194&amp;p=200#p200"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal">Perfect Your Worship of Allaah Wherever You Are</span></strong><br /><br /><br />*AS-SAHEEHAH (no. 3146):<br />ad – Doolaabee reported in „al – Kunaa‟ (1/179-180) from a hadeeth of Aboo<br />Hurairah - radiyallaahu ‟anhu - who said:<br />“A group of desert – dwellers came to Allaah‟s Messenger  and said: „O<br />Messenger of Allaah! Some companions of the Qur·aan claim that no actions<br />benefit without migration (Hijrah) and fighting jihaad in Allaah‟s cause.‟<br />So Allaah‟s Messenger  said:<br />&lt;&lt;Wherever you are and you perfect your worship of Allaah – then receive the<br />good news of Paradise&gt;&gt;.<br />*Shaikh al – Albaanee said: “This is a „hasan‟ chain of narration…”<br />***<br />[Translated by Aboo Talhah Daawood ibn Ronald Burbank - rahimahullaah]<br /><br /><strong>https://alitisaambissunnah.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/perfect-your-worship-of-allaah-wherever-you-are1.pdf</strong><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=61">ابو عبدالرحمز</a> — Sat Aug 27, 2016 8:51 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
